---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Aminu Abdusalam"
  description="Product Manager at Microsoft. Engineer. Builder."
>
  <section class="hero container">
    <p class="greeting">Hey, I'm Aminu <span class="wave" aria-hidden="true">👋</span></p>
    <h1 class="headline">
      I build <span class="accent">commerce products</span> at Microsoft and Xbox
      <span class="cursor" aria-hidden="true">▊</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Product Manager at Microsoft and an engineer at heart, operating at the intersection of product, engineering, and data. I ship commerce
      experiences for hundreds of millions to a billion customers, and I write about the messy in-between of
      product, engineering, and life.
    </p>

    <div class="terminal" role="presentation">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">~/currently</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <p><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami</p>
        <p class="output">Aminu Abdusalam, PM 2, Consumer Commerce</p>
        <p><span class="prompt">$</span> cat currently.md</p>
        <p class="output">Shipping commerce (Game Pass Premium, Fortnite Crew in XGPU, Ask-a-Parent, Recurring Discounts, mobile app store, fraud remediation).</p>
        <p class="output">Building MCP-based Copilot CLI plugins for the org.</p>
        <p class="output">Exploring the product + engineering sweet spot (see: forward-deployed).</p>
        <p class="output">Time with people I care about. Occasional writer.</p>
        <p><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="blink">▊</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <a href="/projects" class="btn">See what I've built →</a>
      <a href="/writing" class="btn btn-secondary">Read the writing</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-block: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
  }

  .greeting {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .wave {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: wave 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform-origin: 70% 70%;
  }

  @keyframes wave {
    0%, 60%, 100% { transform: rotate(0); }
    10% { transform: rotate(14deg); }
    20% { transform: rotate(-8deg); }
    30% { transform: rotate(14deg); }
    40% { transform: rotate(-4deg); }
    50% { transform: rotate(10deg); }
  }

  .headline {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, var(--fs-4xl));
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-text-strong);
    max-width: 20ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    position: relative;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .accent::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: -4px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.35;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .cursor {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    animation: blink 1s steps(2) infinite;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
  }

  .terminal {
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 640px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .terminal-header {
    background: var(--color-bg-hover);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .dot-red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot-yellow { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot-green { background: #28c840; }

  .terminal-title {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
  }

  .terminal-body p {
    margin-block: 4px;
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
  }

  .prompt {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .output {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .blink {
    animation: blink 1s steps(2) infinite;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-glow);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    border-color: var(--color-border-strong);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text-muted);
    color: var(--color-text-strong);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
  }
</style>
